ntence\": \"I did not really understand what was happening, then I realised he was there.\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1992, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's one thing to party on the field, with your team.\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2048, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I do not like that.'\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2073, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Former Montpellier goalkeeper Geronimo Rulli also attacked the French players and said 'Sometimes there are players who do not know how to win and this is what happens.\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2082, \"end\": 2093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montpellier_HSC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.063226553669074e-15, \"text\": \"Montpellier\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montpellier_HSC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montpellier_HSC\"}, {\"begin\": 2105, \"end\": 2113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Geronimo\", \"score\": 0.9999780296392321, \"rank\": 2.1970843395144862e-05, \"text\": \"Geronimo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Geronimo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Geronimo\"}, {\"begin\": 2138, \"end\": 2144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9687291741188322, \"rank\": 0.0264963645050707, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was completely avoidable, it's not a good image for anyone.\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2308, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As Argentinians, we know that when we win, we celebrate with our people and when we lose, we congratulate our opponents and go home.\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2441, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The truth is that some players do not know h